<ul>
  <li>
    <%= link_to "Enable/disable features", url_for(:action=>"features_enabled", :controller=>"admin") %>
    - select individual features and services that you wish to be enabled or disabled.
  </li>
  <li>
    <%= link_to "Site branding", url_for(:action=>"rebrand", :controller=>"admin") %>
    - change some of the wording, title, links and images to adapt SEEK to suit your project
  </li>
  <li>
    <%= link_to "Homepage setting", url_for(:action=>"home_settings", :controller=>"admin") %>
    - set up the welcome and description of your project, select whether displaying the project news and community news,
    also where to retrieve the news from.
  </li>
  <li>
    <%= link_to "Index page behaviour", url_for(:action=>"pagination", :controller=>"admin") %>
    - control whether individual index pages list all items, or just the latest
  </li>
  <li>
    <%= link_to "Additional settings", url_for(:action=>"others", :controller=>"admin") %>
    - some additional properties, such as controls over tags and the email used for DOI and PubMed
  </li>
</ul>